Enum Class DesignPattern.Category

All Implemented Interfaces:

Enclosing class:
DesignPattern
public static enum DesignPattern.Category extends Enum<DesignPattern.Category>
Represents high-level categories of software design patterns.

Each category groups patterns with similar purposes and responsibilities. These categories can help developers understand, organize, and communicate design decisions more effectively.
